name: UOnsetNRTSettings
doc:
UOnsetNRTSettings

Settings for a UOnsetNRT analyzer.

bDownmixToMono: If true, multichannel audio is downmixed to mono with equal amplitude scaling. If false, each channel gets it's own onset result.
GranularityInSeconds: Onset timestamp granularity onsets. Lower granularity takes longer to compute.
Sensitivity: Sensitivity of onset detector. Higher sensitivity will find more onsets.
